---

`.gitignore` (Python / ML)

```gitignore
# ===============================
# Python
# ===============================
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
.env
.venv/
venv/

# ===============================
# Data files
# ===============================
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xls

# ===============================
# Model / cache files
# ===============================
*.pkl
*.joblib
*.npy

# ===============================
# Logs / temp files
# ===============================
*.log
*.tmp
*.out

# ===============================
# OS files
# ===============================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ===============================
# Editors
# ===============================
.vscode/
